2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fbihar-nalanda-men-bury-girl-alive-for-objecting-to-harassment-she-survives-4962011%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20Linked%20To%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20Gang%20Shot%20Dead%20Outside%20Gym%20Near%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20man%20linked%20to%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%20was%20shot%20dead%20outside%20a%20gym%20in%20Faridabad%20near%20Delhi.%20The%20victim%2C%20identified%20as%20Surjabhan%20alias%20Ballu%2C%20was%20shot%20from%20a%20close%20range%20by%20unknown%20assailants%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20the%20police%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20near%20a%20busy%20market%20in%20sector-11%20Faridabad%2C%20outside%20the%20gym%20he%20used%20to%20go%20to.%20Police%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20that%20Ballu%20was%20closely%20associated%20with%20gangster%20Kapil%20Sangwan%20of%20the%20Nandu%20gang%20and%20the%20latter%20had%20links%20with%20dreaded%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%2C%20who%20is%20reportedly%20hiding%20in%20the%20USA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%206%20pm%20today%2C%20the%20victim%20left%20the%20gym%20after%20completing%20his%20workout%20and%20started%20his%20bike.%20Two%20people%20came%20in%20a%20white%20car%20and%20fired%2020%20rounds%20on%20the%20man%20from%20behind%20and%20fled%20the%20scene%2C%20the%20police%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20suspect%20a%20rivalry%20between%20the%20victim%20and%20the%20accused.%20The%20police%20said%20the%20victim%20belonged%20to%20Delhi's%20Najafgarh%20and%20had%20been%20coming%20to%20the%20gym%20in%20Faridabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWitness%20Account%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20man%20shook%20hands%20with%20us%20and%20left%20the%20gym%20around%206%3A20%20pm.%20After%20a%20few%20seconds%2C%20we%20heard%20the%20sound%20of%20gunshots%20and%20ran%20downstairs%20to%20see%20what%20happened%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20gym%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20lying%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20we%20tried%20to%20pick%20him%20up%2C%20but%20he%20was%20already%20dead.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gym%20owner%20said%20that%20the%20man%20had%20been%20coming%20to%20the%20gym%20for%20the%20last%20four%20months%20and%20requested%20them%20not%20to%20reveal%20his%20whereabouts%20to%20anyone%20citing%20a%20threat%20to%20his%20life%20due%20to%20a%20rivalry.%20The%20victim%20reportedly%20told%20the%20owner%20that%20he%20is%20not%20allowed%20to%20go%20to%20Delhi%20because%20of%20the%20rivalry%20and%20because%20of%20this%2C%20he%20is%20living%20in%20Faridabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20told%20us%20that%20he%20is%20an%20Instagram%20influencer%20and%20said%20he%20had%20a%20gun%2C%20but%20we%20never%20saw%20him%20bringing%20it%20to%20the%20gym%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20owner%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20team%20is%20probing%20the%20case%20from%20two%20angles%3A%20Inter%20gang%20rivalry%20and%20Ballu%20going%20against%20Kapil%20Sangwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurajbhan%20is%20closely%20associated%20with%20Kapil%20Sangwan%20and%20is%20responsible%20for%20collecting%20money%20for%20the%20gang.%20A%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20Nandu's%20brother-in-law%20was%20shot%20dead%20inside%20Ballu's%20office%20by%20Manjeet%20Mahal%20from%20a%20rival%20gang%20in%20Delhi's%20Najafgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAngle%201%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Nandu%20asked%20Surajbhan%20to%20testify%20against%20Mahal%20in%20court%2C%20the%20man%20refused%20and%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20that%20Nandu%2C%20who%20is%20hiding%20in%20the%20USA%2C%20may%20have%20decided%20to%20kill%20his%20associate%20for%20breaking%20his%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAngle%202%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurajbhan%20was%20the%20sole%20witness%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20Nandu's%20brother-in-law.%20Manjeet%2C%20who%20is%20lodged%20in%20Delhi's%20Tihar%20Jail%2C%20conspired%20with%20his%20associates%20from%20the%20prison%20to