-to-a-still-durable-labour-market%2Famp_articleshow%2F107269771.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-job-openings-rose-in-december-pointing-to-a-still-durable-labour-market%2Famp_articleshow%2F107269771.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Flag%20Row%2C%20Trouble%20Over%20Board%20Naming%20VD%20Savarkar%20In%20Karnataka%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAnother%20controversy%20has%20engulfed%20Karnataka's%20Uttara%20Kannada%20district%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20Mandya%20flag%20controversy.%20This%20involved%20the%20removal%20of%20a%20right%20wing%20flag%20and%20a%20board%20bearing%20the%20name%20of%20right%20wing%20icon%20VD%20Savarkar.%20A%20protest%20took%20place%20over%20the%20removal%20in%20Bhatkal's%20Tenginagundi%20today%20and%20the%20local%20BJP%20workers%20and%20panchayat%20members%20got%20into%20an%20altercation%20with%20panchayat%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20workers%20argued%20that%20VD%20Savarkar's%20name%20board%20was%20installed%20with%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20panchayat%2C%20and%20they%20protested%20against%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20flagpole%20with%20the%20right%20wing%20flags.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20claimed%20that%20no%20permission%20was%20sought%20from%20the%20gram%20panchayat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20think%20we%20are%20sitting%20quiet.%20We%20have%20permission.%20Is%20it%20a%20Pakistan%20flag%20that%20we%20put%20up%3F%20Who%20gave%20you%20the%20order%20to%20raze%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20of%20the%20angry%20villagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Zilla%20Panchayat%20chief%2C%20along%20with%20senior%20authorities%2C%20decided%20to%20issue%20notices%20for%20all%20such%20structures%20built%20in%20the%20area%20under%20the%20panchayat.%20They%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20stay%20only%20if%20they%20have%20the%20necessary%20permissions%20from%20local%20administration%20or%20local%20taluks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20mandatory%20documents%20are%20not%20produced%20within%2015%20days%2C%20the%20structures%20will%20be%20razed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20decided%20to%20issue%20notices%20to%20all%20such%20structures%20in%20that%20panchayat.%20If%20they%20have%20the%20necessary%20permissions%20from%20local%20administration%20or%20local%20taluks%2C%20they%20will%20be%20considered.%3Cbr%3E%5CnOtherwise%2C%2015%20days%20time%20will%20be%20given%20to%20produce%20documents.%20If%20not%2C%20unauthorised%20structures%20and%20nameboards%20will%20be%20removed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ishwar%20Kumar%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20Zilla%20Parishad.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnLast%20week%2C%20a%20saffron%20Hanuman%20flag%20hoisted%20by%20a%20local%20religious%20organisation%2C%20was%20taken%20down%20leading%20to%20huge%20row%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Keragodu%20and%20nearby%20areas%20of%20Mandya%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20led%20to%20widespread%20protests%20that%20escalated%20into%20a%20political%20conflict%20between%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20and%20the%20opposition%20BJP%20and%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20of%20HD%20Kumaraswamy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flag%20was%20funded%20and%20set%20up%20by%20a%20section%20of%20villagers%20near%20a%20temple.%20Reports%20indicated%20the%20BJP%20and%20JDS%20were%20also%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20many%20people%20held%20protests%20and%20complained%20to%20the%20district%20administration%2C%20which%20later%20removed%20the%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706632860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F7mh724sk_karnataka-savarkar-board-row_625x300_30_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-flag-row-trouble-over-board-naming-vd-savarkar-in-karnataka-4962143%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Another%20controversy%20has%20engulfed%20Karnataka's%20Uttara%20Kannada%20district%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20Mandya%20flag%20controversy.%20This%20involved%20the%20removal%20of%20a%20right%20wing%20flag%20and%20a%20