20a%20remarkable%20comeback%20to%20win%20the%20game%20by%2028%20runs%20and%20go%201-0%20up%20in%20the%20five-match%20series.%20Jadeja%20snapped%20up%20five%20wickets%20and%20made%2087%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20while%20Rahul%20scored%2086.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJadeja's%20all-round%20abilities%20are%20invaluable%20to%20the%20team.%20Off-spinner%20Sundar%2C%20who%20has%20shown%20a%20lot%20of%20promise%20in%20his%20four-Test%20old%20career%2C%20could%20replace%20Jadeja%20in%20the%20playing%20eleven.%20Ever%20since%20making%20his%20comeback%20from%20injury%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20in%20September%2C%20Rahul%20has%20displayed%20stellar%20form%20in%20the%20ODI%20and%20Test%20format.%20Keeping%20wickets%20in%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20and%20more%20recently%20in%20the%20Test%20series%20in%20South%20Africa%20added%20to%20his%20workload.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706627160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fdtb86u5_sarfaraz-khan_625x300_29_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsarfaraz-khans-act-one-day-after-earning-maiden-test-call-up-leaves-fans-in-awe-4958690%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sarfaraz%20Khan%20went%20straight%20to%20the%20practice%20ground%20after%20earning%20his%20maiden%20Test%20call-up%20in%20the%20Indian%20team.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Ravan%20Triumphs%20in%20Ayodhya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22170459%2FGEb7QB7bMAA0uXA.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EJanuary%2022%2C%202024%2C%20was%20a%20historic%20day.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20sad%20day%2C%20but%20a%20historic%20day%20nonetheless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20sad%20day%20because%20along%20with%20the%20idol%20of%20the%20Maryada%20Purushottam%20in%20Ayodhya%20was%20also%20enshrined%20a%20new%20idea%20of%20India.%20An%20idea%20that%20recognises%20only%20one%20native%2C%20authentic%2C%20and%20legitimate%20version%20of%20India%20and%20views%20every%20other%20culture%2C%20belief%2C%20religion%2C%20and%20morality%20as%20interlopers%20to%20be%20at%20best%20tolerated%20and%20at%20worse%20put%20in%20their%20placed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20M.%20S.%20Golwalkar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsanjeev.sabhlokcity.com%2FMisc%2FWe-or-Our-Nationhood-Defined-Shri-M-S-Golwalkar.pdf%5C%22%3Eput%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6in%20this%20country%2C%20Hindustan%2C%20the%20Hindu%20Race%20with%20its%20Hindu%20Religion%2C%20Hindu%20Culture%20and%20Hindu%20Language%2C%20(the%20natural%20family%20of%20Sanskrit%20and%20her%20off-%20springs)%20complete%20the%20Nation%20concept%E2%80%A6in%20Hindustan%20exists%20and%20must%20needs%20exist%20the%20ancient%20Hindu%20nation%20and%20naught%20else%20but%20the%20Hindu%20Nation.%20All%20those%20not%20belonging%20to%20the%20national%20i.e.%20Hindu%20Race%2C%20Religion%2C%20Culture%20and%20Language%2C%20naturally%20fall%20out%20of%20the%20pale%20of%20real%20%E2%80%98National%E2%80%99%20life.%E2%80%9D%20In%20this%20Idea%20of%20India%2C%20adherents%20of%20this%20one%20India%20have%20first%20and%20absolute%20right%20over%20her%20destiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%2C%20in%20M.%20S.%20Golwalkar%E2%80%99s%20chilling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsanjeev.sabhlokcity.com%2FMisc%2FWe-or-Our-Nationhood-Defined-Shri-M-S-Golwalkar.pdf%5C%22%3Ewords%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6(minorities)%20in%20Hindusthan%20must%20either%20adopt%20the%20Hindu%20culture%20and%20language%2C%20must%20learn%20to%20respect%20and%20hold%20in%20reverence%20Hindu%20religion%2C%20must%20entertain%20no%20idea%20but%20those%20of%20the%20glorification%20of%20the%20Hindu%20race%20and%20culture%2C%20i.e.%2C%20of%20the%20Hindu%20nation%20and%20must%20lose%20their%20separate%20existence%20to%20merge%20in%20the%20Hindu%20race%2C%20or%20may%20stay%20in%20the%20country%2C%20wholly%20subordinated%20to%20the%20Hindu%20Nation%2C%20claiming%20nothing%2C%20deserving%20no%20privileges%2C%20far%20less%20any%20preferential%20treatment%20%E2%80%93%20not%20even%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20rights%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20idea%20of%20India%2C%20the%20majority%20may%20use%20any%20means%20they%20choose%20to%20impose%20their%20desire%20upon%20the%20rest%20of%20us.%20This%20bulldozing%20of%20multiplicities%20and%20the%20dominance%20of%20the%20majority%20is%20regarded%20not%20just%20as%20legitimate%20but%20indeed%20patriotic%2C%20which%20brings%20us%20to%20the%20greatest%20tragedy%20of%20all.%20It%20is%20an%20idea%20of%20India%2C%20that%20dwarfs%20the%20spiritual%20universe%20of%20its%20people.%20It%20produces%20petty%20bullies%20full%20of%20fear%2C%20hate%2C%20insecurity%2C%20and%20suspicion%20who%20find%20validation%20in%20kicking%20their%20fellow%20countrymen%20in%20the%20teeth.%20The%20products%20of%20this%20idea%20of%20India%20can%20be%20true%20to%20neither%20their%20religion%20nor%20their%20nation%20nor%20indeed%20to%20their%20own%20full%20potential%20as%20human%20beings.%20The%20temple%20may%20have%20been%20dedicated%20to%20Ram%2C%20but%20it%20is%20Ravan%20who%20seems%20to%20have%20triumphed%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJan%2022%20was%20also%20a%20historic%20day.%20It%20was%20historic%20because%20this%20idea%20of%20India%20was%20celebrated%20that%20day%20not%20by%20a%20marginal%20group%20of%20private%20individuals%20or%20organizations%20but%20by%20the%20Indian%20state%2C%20its%20elected%20leadership%20and%20nearly%20every%20institution%20and%20domain%20with%20social%20power.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20the%20few%20who%20refused%20to%20celebrate%20the%20day%20that%20found%20themselves%20at%20the%20margins.%20It%20is%20this%20collective%20celebration%20of%20the%20powerful%20that%20made%20the%20event%20a%20consecration%20of%20a%20new%20idea%20of%20India.%20The%20elected%20government%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20the%20administrative%20machinery%20made%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20edifice%20their%20personal%20project.%20The%20judiciary%20legitimized%20the%20project%20with%20its%20judgement%20and%20most%20of%20the%20media%20dedicated%20itself%20to%20the%20breathless%20celebration%20and%20a%20bevy%20of%20celebrities%20lent%20their%20prestige%20and%20respectability%20to%20the%20event.%20Even%20the%20armed%20forces%20joined%20the%20party%20by%20showering%20the%20venue%20with%20flowers.%20But%20the%20ultimate%20consecration%20was%20in%20the%20popular%20imagination%2C%20visible%20in%20the%20form%20of%20florescent%20pinkish-orange%20flags%20that%20took%20over%20our%20public%20spaces.%20These%20were%20not%20the%20pennants%20of%20fervent%20devotees.%20They%20were%20instead%20the%20standards%20of%20conquerors%20showing%20the%20rest%20of%20us%20our%20place%20in%20the%20new%20dispensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20145109%2Fimage-1771.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221128%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20145109%2Fimage-1771.png%201128w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20145109%2Fimage-1771-300x186.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20145109%2Fimage-1771-1024x635.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20road%20to%20Ayodhya.%20Photo%3A%20Ananta%20Jain%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20of%20us%20who%20disagree%20with%20this%20idea%20of%20India%20have%20responded%20to%20the%20events%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20approach%20has%20been%20to%20deny%20that%20the%20day%20was%20sad%20at%20all.%20It%20welcomes%20and%20celebrates%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20edifice%20in%20Ayodhya%20reserving%20its%20criticism%20only%20for%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20ceremony%20was%20conducted.%20Rather%20than%20object%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20riotous%20mob%20broke%20laws%2C%20violated%20human%20decency%20and%20mangled%20the%20national%20fabric%20to%20destroy%20a%20mosque%20and%20make%20way%20for%20the%20temple%2C%20it%20objects%20only%20to%20who%20was%20invited%20and%20who%20presided%20over%20the%20consecration.%20This%20is%20akin%20to%20criticizing%20the%20d%C3%A9cor%20of%20a%20building%20constructed%20on%20stolen%20land.%20Would%20the%20project%20have%20been%20any%20more%20legitimate%20if%20it%20was%20conducted%20in%20strict%20accordance%20with%20scriptures%20without%20a%20BJP%20leader%20or%20flag%20in%20sight%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20view%20denies%20that%20the%20day%20was%20historic%20at%20all.%20It%20sees%20the%20event%20at%20Ayodhya%20as%20just%20another%20in%20a%20string%20unconstitutional%20acts%20rather%20than%20as%20the%20consummation%20of%20a%20long%20project%20to%20establish%20a%20new%20order.%20It%20takes%20refuge%20in%20the%20existence%20of%20the%20Constitution%20without%20recognizing%20that%20the%20Constitution%20itself%20has%20been%20usurped%20and%20confined%20to%20the%20pages%20it%20is%20written%20on.%20It%20holds%20hope%20in%20electoral%20arithmetic%20without%20recognising%20that%20a%20change%20in%20government%20does%20not%20necessarily%20imply%20a%20change%20in%20the%20order%20of%20things.%20It%20tiptoes%20around%20the%20venom%20that%20has%20seized%20our%20national%20consciousness%20and%20hopes%20that%20a%20variety%20of%20side%20narratives%20can%20somehow%20dilute%20the%20poison.%20But%20that%20is%20a%20denial%20of%20the%20challenge%20that%20stands%20before%20us%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20compelling%20logic%20for%20these%20positions.%20They%20come%20from%20the%20desire%20to%20preserve%20an%20existence%20in%20the%20new%20political%20mainstream%20so%20that%20we%20may%20survive%20to%20fight%20another%20day.%20But%20they%20come%20at%20the%20price%20of%20accepting%20and%20unwillingly%20legitimizing%20the%20new%20order.%20A%20price%20that%20I%20find%20too%20much%20to%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20propose%20another%20position.%20It%20is%20to%20call%20out%20and%20stand%20firm%20against%20the%20madness%20that%20has%20seized%20the%20Nation.%20This%20position%20requires%20us%20to%20recognize%20the%20human%2C%20constitutional%2C%20and%20spiritual%20tragedy%20that%20is%20the%20event%20in%20Ayodhya.%20It%20requires%20us%20to%20reject%20the%20idea%20that%20what%20happened%20at%20Ayodhya%20represents%20divinity%2C%20justice%2C%20or%20patriotism%20in%20any%20form%20whatsoever.%20It%20requires%20us%20to%20reject%20the%20cheap%20counterfeit%20being%20peddled%20in%20Ayodhya%20as%20being%20Hinduism%20or%20the%20worship%20of%20Ram.%20It%20requires%20us%20to%20reject%20the%20idea%20that%20vengeance%20perpetrated%20upon%20our%20countrymen%20of%20today%20for%20the%20sins%2C%20real%20and%20imagined%2C%20of%20their%20co-religionists%20of%20the%20past%20can%20in%20any%20way%20be%20called%20justice.%20It%20requires%20us%20to%20reject%20the%20idea%20that%20what%20is%20wrong%20by%20any%20standard%20of%20humanity%20becomes%20right%20because%20a%20compromised%20justice%20system%20and%20a%20bevy%20of%20celebrities%20say%20it%20to%20be%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20position%20also%20requires%20us%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20Ayodhya%20is%20more%20than%20just%20another%20event%20but%20is%20in%20fact%20the%20harbinger%20of%20a%20new%2C%20sinister%20idea%20of%20our%20nationhood.%20It%20requires%20us%20to%20recognise%20that%20the%20struggle%20is%20for%20something%20much%20greater%20than%20the%20outcome%20of%20one%20election%2C%20it%20is%20a%20struggle%20for%20how%20India%20understands%20itself%20and%20its%20purpose.%20This%20is%20a%20task%20that%20will%20be%20long%20and%20very%20often%20lonely.%20But%20most%20of%20all%20it%20requires%20us%20to%20stand%20publicly%20and%20somewhat%20outnumbered%20but%20without%20despair%2C%20anger%20or%20fear%20for%20what%20we%20believe%20to%20be%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20in%20this%20position%20could%20indeed%20find%20ourselves%20to%20be%20irrelevant%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98mainstream%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20new%20order%2C%20but%20in%20the%20exile%20of%20this%20irrelevance%20lies%20the%20possibility%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20remote%2C%20of%20becoming%20relevant%20in%20a%20politics%20of%20our%20choosing%20than%20in%20playing%20the%20domesticated%20roles%20in%20a%20politics%20we%20do%20not%20believe%20in.%20We%20could%20also%20be%20accused%20of%20standing%20against%20the%20tide%20of%20history.%20But%20in%20that%20resistance%20lies%20the%20possibility%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20remote%2C%20of%20writing%20a%20history%20of%20our%20own.%C2%A0Jai%20Jagat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESachin%20Rao%20is%20a%20Congress%20Worker%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706626853000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22170459%2FGEb7QB7bMAA0uXA.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwhen-ravan-triumphs-in-ayodhya%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22January%2022%2C%202024%20was%20a%20sad%20day%20because%20along%20with%20the%20idol%20of%20the%20Maryada%20Purushottam%20in%20Ayodhya%20was%20also%20enshrined%20a%20new%20idea%20of%20India%2C%20where%20the%20majority%20can%20use%20any%20means%20to%20impose%20their%20desire%20upon%20the%20rest%20of%20us.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwhen-ravan-triumphs-in-ayodhya%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NDTV%20Q3%20results%3A%20Net%20loss%20at%20Rs%2010.16%20cr%2C%20revenue%20falls%207%25%20to%20Rs%20