%80%99%2C%20in%20Araria%20district%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20broke%20his%20silence%20on%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20flip-flop%20back%20into%20the%20BJP%20camp%20at%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Purnea.%20He%20started%20with%20the%20now%20well-known%20joke%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar%20forgetting%20his%20shawl%20at%20Raj%20Bhawan%20after%20presenting%20himself%20to%20reconstitute%20his%20government%20with%20the%20BJP%20this%20time.%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20Chhatisgarh%2C%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20had%20just%20narrated%20the%20joke%20to%20him.%20The%20joke%20goes%20that%20when%20Kumar%20turned%20up%20to%20pick%20up%20his%20shawl%2C%20the%20governor%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eitni%20jaldi%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20(back%20so%20soon%20to%20again%20change%20camps%3F).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joke%20got%20many%20laughs%20as%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20underlined%20that%20INDIA%20would%20continue%20to%20stand%20for%20backward%20classes%20and%20for%20social%20justice%20in%20Bihar.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fbharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-reaches-purnia-on-day-2-in-bihar-rahul-to-address-rally%2Farticle67791928.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20said%20the%20alliance%20does%20not%20need%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20for%20the%20cause.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%E2%80%98Mahagathbandhan%E2%80%99%20(grand%20alliance)%20will%20fight%20for%20social%20justice%20in%20Bihar%3B%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20Nitish%20Kumar%20for%20that%20purpose%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20him%20at%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Congress%20leader%20is%20reported%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F-3DtTN85FoU%3Fsi%3DAxxwPUkwZmHKQWFj%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data