2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20134258%2FF80iGYpasAEo0kc.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680992%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22427%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20month%20before%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20BC%20declaration%20at%20Kamareddy%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20said%20a%20caste%20survey%20would%20be%20held%20if%20the%20party%20came%20to%20power.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40INCTelangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20caste%20survey%20was%20largely%20a%20sequel%20to%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20stand%20on%20equitable%20social%20justice%20as%20decided%20at%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-chintan-shivir-udaipur-bharat-jodo%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Echintan%20shivir%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20at%20Udaipur%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20often%20raised%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20later%2C%20its%20purpose%20in%20Telangana%20seemed%20to%20be%20to%20target%20the%20BCs%20and%20bring%20them%20back%20to%20the%20party%20fold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20128%20castes%20among%20the%20BCs%20in%20Telangana.%20They%20constitute%20more%20than%2050%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20but%20unlike%20the%20SCs%20and%20STs%2C%20they%20lacked%20a%20homogenous%20character.%20The%20BCs%20had%20distanced%20themselves%20from%20the%20Congress%20and%20moved%20closer%20to%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20prior%20to%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20formation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20had%20consolidated%20these%20gains%20by%20launching%20several%20welfare%20programmes%20for%20the%20section.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20formation%20and%20the%20TDP%20becoming%20weak%2C%20the%20BJP%20attracted%20the%20BCs%20as%20part%20of%20its%20polarisation%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samiti%20(TRS)%2C%20now%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%2C%20tried%20to%20strike%20an%20emotional%20chord%20with%20the%20BCs%20by%20holding%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eatmeeya%20sammelan%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20meetings%20(meetings%20of%20camaraderie)%20with%20different%20castes%20separately%20to%20build%20a%20vote%20bank%20in%20the%20assembly%20and%20parliament%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20were%20found%20wanting%20in%20wooing%20the%20section%20in%20this%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficial%20sources%20were%20optimistic%20that%20the%20survey%20will%20aid%20in%20revising%20reservations%20for%20BCs%20in%20gram%20panchayats%2C%20zilla%20parishads%20and%20municipalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20mobile%20app%20with%20the%20details%20of%20all%20castes%20and%20sub-castes%20will%20be%20created%20for%20enumeration%20and%20care%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20avoid%20the%20charge%20of%20bias%20as%20faced%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%20in%20its%20survey%2C%20the%20sources%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30173458%2FSammelanam-1024x768.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30173458%2FSammelanam-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30173458%2FSammelanam-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30173458%2FSammelanam.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694960%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20BRS%20tried%20to%20strike%20an%20emotional%20chord%20with%20BCs%20with%20their%20%E2%80%98atmeeya%20sammelan%E2%80%99%20meetings.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40PuranamSatish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbihar-caste-census-released-at-63-obc-ebc-groups-set-to-take-pole-position-in-state-politics%5C%22%3EBihar%E2%80%99s%20caste%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20the%20BC%20population%20in%20the%20state%20to%20be%20around%2063%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajya%20Sabha%20member%20and%20prominent%20BC%20leader%20R.%20Krishnaiah%20said%20there%20were%20a%20number%20of%20court%20cases%20challenging%20reservations%20in%20local%20bodies%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20scientific%20data%20about%20the%20population%20of%20BCs.%20Population-based%20allocation%20of%20funds%20for%20corporations%20and%20federations%20assisting%20people%20in%20the%20traditional%20occupations%20of%20their%20castes%20was%20also%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20previous%20BRS%20government%20had%20taken%20up%20a%20one-day%20comprehensive%20household%20survey%20in%20the%20state%20shortly%20after%20assuming%20the%20reins%20in%202014%2C%20but%20its%20report%20had%20never%20seen%20the%20light%20of%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20unofficial%20claims%20put%20the%20population%20of%20SCs%20in%20Telangana%20at%2018%25%2C%20STs%20at%2010%25%2C%20other%20castes%20at%2021%25%20and%20BCs%20at%2051%25%20as%20per%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20led%20to%20a%20demand%20by%20the%20SCs%20to%20hike%20their%20quota%20in%20education%20and%20employment%20to%2018%25%20in%20tune%20with%20their%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SCs%20led%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fahead-of-telangana-polls-pm-modi-sets-in-motion-madiga-sub-categorisation-process-report%5C%22%3EMadiga%20Reservation%20Porata%20Samiti%20(MRPS)%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20also%20been%20demanding%20their%20categorisation%20into%20four%20groups%20%E2%80%93%20A%2C%20B%2C%20C%20and%20D%20%E2%80%93%20since%201994.%20The%20categorisation%20was%20implemented%20for%20some%20time%20during%20the%20chief%20ministership%20of%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20but%20withdrawn%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdespite-caste-survey-politics-is-obc-vote-eluding-india%5C%22%3EDespite%20Caste%20Survey%20Politics%2C%20Is%20OBC%20Vote%20Eluding%20INDIA%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20again%20constituted%20a%20committee%20of%20secretaries%20headed%20by%20the%20cabinet%20secretary%20to%20go%20into%20the%20categorisation%20of%20SCs%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20conceded%20to%20the%20demand%20of%20MRPS%20president%20Manda%20Krishna%20Madiga%20at%20an%20election%20rally%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Hyderabad%20for%20the%20weaker%20sections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAided%20by%20the%20survey%2C%20the%20Congress%20could%20hope%20to%20hijack%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20place%20in%20supporting%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20categorisation%20of%20SCs%20ahead%20of%20general%20elections.%20The%20party%20had%20also%20conceded%20to%20the%20demand%20of%2018%25%20reservation%20for%20SCs%20and%20their%20categorisation%20into%20four%20groups%20named%20A%2C%20B%2C%20C%20and%20D%20in%20its%20manifesto.%20It%20also%20promised%20reservations%20for%20minorities%20and%20finance%20corporations%20for%20all%20BC%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20Congress%20minister%20who%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20named%20said%20the%20survey%20will%20help%20the%20government%20in%20extending%20largesse%20proportional%20to%20the%20population%20of%20the%20concerned%20groups.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20benefits%20were%20cornered%20by%20dominant%20caste%20groups%20like%20the%20Madigas%20among%20the%20SCs%20and%20the%20Munnuru%20Kapus%20among%20the%20BCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Congress%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20V.%20Hanumantha%20Rao%20expected%20the%20SCs%2C%20STs%20and%20BCs%20to%20back%20the%20party%20in%20a%20big%20way%20after%20the%20survey%20as%20%C2%A0an%20equitable%20quota%20system%20would%20be%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16141604%2FThe-Wire-82-1024x478.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16141604%2FThe-Wire-82-1024x478.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16141604%2FThe-Wire-82-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16141604%2FThe-Wire-82.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685050%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22392%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Congress%20could%20hope%20to%20hijack%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20place%20in%20supporting%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20categorisation%20of%20SCs%20ahead%20of%20general%20elections.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FNarendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelangana%20has%20never%20had%20clean%20data%20on%20the%20socio-economic%20status%20of%20its%20population%20since%201931%2C%20when%20a%20census%20was%20conducted%20during%20British%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chairman%20of%20the%20Telangana%20State%20Backward%20Classes%20Commission%2C%20V.%20Krishnamohan%20Rao%2C%20has%20warned%20about%20the%20danger%20of%20bias%20in%20the%20survey%20as%20happened%20in%20Bihar%20if%20the%20government%20were%20to%20conduct%20the%20survey%20through%20its%20departments.%20The%20commission%20was%20the%20competent%20authority%20for%20the%20purpose%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalled%20that%20a%20socio-economic%20survey%20by%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance-II%20government%20in%202011-14%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20was%20dropped%20by%20the%20subsequent%20BJP%20government%20as%20it%20was%20found%20that%20there%20were%20errors%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20details%20of%20forty%20million%20individuals%20in%20the%20survey%20taken%20up%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Rural%20Development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20some%20high%20courts%20had%20struck%20down%20the%20surveys%20as%20they%20lacked%20scientific%20validity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishnamohan%20Rao%20felt%20that%20social%20indicators%20like%20discrimination%2C%20financial%20status%20and%20the%20representation%20of%20targeted%20groups%20in%20various%20spheres%20could%20be%20thoroughly%20studied%20by%20commissions%20of%20inquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20retired%20bureaucrat%2C%20N.%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%2C%20dubbed%20the%20survey%20as%20a%20retrograde%20step%20for%20political%20gains.%20It%20was%20nothing%20but%20another%20attempt%20to%20divide%20people%20on%20caste%20lines%20instead%20of%20making%20them%20less%20caste%20conscious%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20reservation%20on%20affirmative%20political%20action%20did%20not%20require%20a%20caste%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20disagreed%20with%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20claim%20that%20the%20survey%20was%20meant%20to%20identify%20beneficiaries%20for%20its%20welfare%20schemes.%20Better%20selection%20of%20beneficiaries%20was%20unrelated%20to%20caste%20survey%20going%20by%20past%20experience%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706620671000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30182304%2FTelangana-prabhutvam-II.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-congress-govts-preparations-for-caste-survey-in-full-swing-as-lok-sabha-polls-inch-closer%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Official%20sources%20expressed%20optimism%20that%20the%20survey%20would%20help%20revise%20reservations%20for%20the%20state's%20backward%20class%20communities%2C%20while%20others%20cautioned%20against%20accusations%20of%20bias%20or%20said%20the%20exercise%20was%20for%20political%20gain.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%2