%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20said%20the%20accused%20woman%20was%20not%20cooperating%20in%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20initially%20told%20the%20police%20that%20she%20is%20a%20doctor%20and%20that%20her%20husband%2C%20too%2C%20is%20a%20doctor%20and%20lives%20in%20New%20York%2C%20however%20this%20information%20is%20also%20yet%20to%20be%20established%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJhansi%20Rani%20Samuel%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Delhi%20police%20on%20January%2013%20following%20a%20PCR%20call%20by%20the%20hotel%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20initially%20arrested%20for%20cheating%20but%20later%20Sections%20419%20(punishment%20for%20cheating%20by%20impersonation)%2C%20468%20(forgery%20for%20purpose%20of%20cheating)%20and%20471%20(using%20as%20genuine%20a%20forged%20document)%20of%20the%20IPC%20were%20added%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20the%20official%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706620620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fglstdhpg_pullman-hotel-delhi_625x300_30_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fshe-ran-up-a-bill-of-rs-6-lakh-at-delhi-hotel-had-only-rs-41-in-her-account-4960946%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20woman%20who%20was%20recently%20arrested%20for%20cheating%20a%20luxury%20hotel%20in%20Delhi's%20Aerocity%20of%20around%20Rs%206%20lakh%20had%20only%20Rs%2041%20in%20her%20account%20after%20she%20was%20arrested%2C%20police%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fshe-ran-up-a-bill-of-rs-6-lakh-at-delhi-hotel-had-only-rs-41-in-her-account-4960946%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fshe-ra