entral%20schemes%20for%20the%20respective%20state%20and%20finally%20inaugurating%20a%20couple%20of%20Union%20government%20programmes.%20This%20is%20the%20standard%20itinerary%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20southern%20forays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20already%20covered%20temples%20like%20Tirupathi%20and%20Veerbhadra%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Ranganathswamy%20and%20Rameshwaram%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Guruvayur%20and%20Thriprayar%20in%20Kerala.%20At%20all%20these%20places%2C%20he%20had%20road%20shows%20and%20political%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20present%20schedule%2C%20about%20140%20Modi%20rallies%20have%20been%20lined%20up%20across%20the%20country%20during%20the%20next%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeeks%20before%20a%20PM%20visit%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20the%20security%20officials%20do%20is%20to%20persuade%20the%20media%20not%20to%20carry%20adverse%20reports%20and%20the%20details%20of%20security%20measures%20in%20%E2%80%98national%20interest.%E2%80%99%20Thus%2C%20people%20come%20to%20know%20about%20the%20rigorous%20traffic%20restrictions%20and%20omnipresent%20barricades%20only%20when%20they%20appear%20along%20the%20long%20stretch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%2022%2C000%20police%20personnel%20were%20deployed%20in%20Chennai%20when%20Modi%20came%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20Khelo%20India%20Youth%20games%20as%20part%20of%20a%20five-layer%20security%20for%20the%20PM.%20This%20is%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20SPG%20and%20an%20army%20of%20security%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30170059%2FGEN1cm9bIAAMIAu.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221137%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30170059%2FGEN1cm9bIAAMIAu.jpg%201137w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30170059%2FGEN1cm9bIAAMIAu-284x300.jpg%20284w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30170059%2FGEN1cm9bIAAMIAu-970x1024.jpg%20970w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694954%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20the%20inauguration%20of%20Khelo%20India%20Youth%20Games%20in%20Chennai%20on%20January%2019%2C%202024.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40narendramodi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Srirangam%2C%20it%20was%203%2C500%20plus%20security%20paraphernalia.%20At%20Guruvayur%2C%202%2C000%20police%20personnel%20were%20deployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20level%20of%20security%20for%20former%20PMs%2C%20including%20Vajpayee%20during%20the%20Kargil%20war%2C%20was%20a%20fraction%20of%20what%20Modi%20has.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Guruvayur%2C%20traffic%20halted%20on%20all%20artery%20roads%20to%20the%20temple%20town%20for%20about%20ten%20kms%20for%2018%20hours%20before%20Modi%20arrived%20at%20a%20helipad%20hurriedly%20built%20at%20a%20school%20ground.%20There%20was%20also%20a%20rehearsal%20before%20this.%20This%20meant%20about%20a%20hundred%20vehicles%2C%20some%20from%20outside%20the%20state%2C%20held%20up%20outside%20the%20sanitized%20periphery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20governors%20of%20southern%20states%20had%20also%20come%20to%20meet%20Modi.%20Their%20security%20also%20added%20to%20the%20disruption.%20Traffic%20police%20had%20announced%20details%20of%20traffic%20diversions%20at%20the%20last%20minute.%20Buses%20along%20the%20route%20carrying%20officegoers%20in%20the%20morning%20got%20delayed.%20Due%20to%20diversions%2C%20many%20passengers%20were%20told%20to%20get%20down%20at%20odd%20places%20far%20away%20from%20their%20destinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20mainstream%20media%20played%20it%20safe%2C%20parallel%20media%20had%20graphic%20details%20of%20patients%20who%20were%20held%20up%20on%20their%20way%20to%20the%20general%20hospital%20at%20Kochi.%20At%20all%20places%2C%20the%20first%20sign%20of%20a%20Modi%20roadshow%20is%20the%20appearance%20of%20barricades.%20At%20Kochi%2C%20the%20barricades%20put%20up%20prevented%20egress%20and%20ingress%20of%20the%20residents%20until%20Modi%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20roadshow%20was%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20it%20held%20up%20a%20large%20number%20of%20those%20returning%20home%20from%20the%20offices.%20The%20disruption%20of%20public%20transport%20made%20it%20worse.%20Many%20had%20to%20walk%20long%20distances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Guruvayur%20Krishna%20temple%20is%20a%20preferred%20place%20for%20initiation%20of%20rice%20feeding%20for%20babies%2C%3Cem%3E%20tulabharam%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20weddings%20%E2%80%94%20a%20practice%20which%20began%20in%20the%20mid-20th%20century%20and%20can%20be%20traced%20to%20church%20marriages.%20Rice%20feeding%20and%20tulabharam%20were%20cancelled%20for%20the%20day%20due%20to%20the%20Modi%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20devotees%2C%20who%20visit%20the%20temple%20from%20faraway%20places%2C%20had%20to%20wait%20outside%20the%20three-layer%20security%20or%20cancel%20it%20on%20that%20auspicious%20day.%20Sabarimala%20pilgrims%2C%20who%20were%20returning%20from%20the%20hill%20temple%20after%20the%20Makaravilakku%2C%20usually%20visit%20Guruvayur.%20Most%20of%20the%20pilgrim%20groups%20had%20to%20cancel%20their%20visit%20or%20wait%20for%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20departure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2080%20marriages%20were%20scheduled%20that%20day.%20At%20the%20last%20minute%2C%2031%20of%20these%20were%20rescheduled%20between%20as%20early%20as%205%20am%20and%206%20am%2C%20a%20safe%20two%20hours%20before%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20arrival.%20Among%20them%20was%20a%20couple%20I%20know%20from%20Vadakkancheri%20whose%20wedding%20was%20originally%20scheduled%20between%208%20am%20and%209%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20pleading%20with%20the%20Devaswam%20board%20chairman%2C%20they%20got%20it%20rescheduled%20between%205%20am%20and%206%20am.%20Adding%20to%20their%20woes%2C%20the%20SPG%20allowed%20only%20four%20persons%20to%20attend.%20The%20groom%E2%80%99s%20and%20brides%E2%80%99%20parties%20had%20invited%20a%20large%20number%20of%20friends%20and%20relatives.%20All%20invitees%2C%20including%20NRI%20relatives%20who%20had%20come%20from%20abroad%2C%20had%20to%20sit%20outside%20the%20three-layer%20security%20ring.%20Reaching%20at%2012%20midnight%2C%20the%20parents%20had%20a%20harrowing%20time%20to%20get%20the%20entry%20passes%20to%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20the%20ceremony%20at%20the%20temple%2C%20the%20parties%20were%20held%20up%20inside%20the%20complex%20as%20the%20SPG%20insisted%20they%20could%20leave%20only%20after%20Modi%20left.%20This%20meant%20they%20were%20held%20up%20for%20five%20hours.%20Earlier%2C%20two%20other%20marriage%20parties%20cancelled%20their%20wedding%20and%20left%20Guruvayur%20in%20a%20huff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20visit%2C%20the%20Guruvayur%20municipality%20and%20adjoining%20five%20panchayats%20closed%20all%20educational%20institutions.%20The%20SPG%20asked%20all%20guest%20houses%20and%20hotels%20to%20provide%20a%20list%20of%20their%20registered%20guests.%20Two%20days%20before%2C%20they%20were%20also%20ordered%20to%20cancel%20all%20registrations%20for%20two%20days%20and%20evict%20the%20guests%20before%20the%20Modi%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20them%20were%20those%20who%20had%20come%20for%20month-long%20observances%20at%20the%20temple.%20Within%20the%20temple%2C%20all%20except%2015%20of%20its%2040-odd%20attendants%20and%20office%20staff%20were%20told%20to%20leave.%20They%20were%20allowed%20in%20only%20after%20Modi%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strategists%20in%20Delhi%20as%20well%20as%20state%20leaders%20maintain%20that%20each%20Modi%20visit%20to%20Kerala%20has%20helped%20the%20party%20make%20inroads%20into%20new%20sections%20of%20people.%20In%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20set%20to%20make%20more%20such%20visits%20to%20Kerala.%20According%20to%20a%20BJP%20leader%2C%20its%20high%20command%20has%20identified%20four%20or%20five%20winnable%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20in%20the%20past%20was%20never%20able%20to%20win%20a%20parliament%20seat.%20It%20had%20its%20lone%20MLA%20in%20the%20previous%20assembly.%20In%20the%20last%20assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20party%20lost%20that%20seat%20too%20and%20the%20BJP%20drew%20a%20blank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20current%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20it%20is%20concentrating%20on%20Thrissur%20where%20it%20is%20hoping%20to%20rely%20on%20the%20popularity%20of%20an%20actor-turned-politician.%20Apart%20from%20superior%20money%20power%2C%20the%20BJP%20high%20command%20expects%20its%20Christian%20outreach%20will%20bear%20fruit%20and%20enable%20it%20to%20win%20over%20local%20church%20leaders.%20This%20could%20tilt%20the%20balance%20in%20many%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EP.%20Raman%20is%20a%20veteran%20journalist%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706619646000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30165616%2FEffect-91.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdissecting-modis-pre-poll-visits-to-the-south%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20per%20the%20present%20schedule%2C%20about%20140%20Modi%20rallies%20have%20been%20lined%20up%20across%20the%20country%20during%20the%20next%20three%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdissecting-modis-pre-poll-visits-to-the-south%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Record-breaking%20Suits%20and%20Bluey%20named%20most-streamed%20shows%20of%202023%20in%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706619297000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F