mpproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Firan-and-the-us-were-once-friends-what-happened-13059917%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Firan-and-the-us-were-once-friends-what-happened-13059917%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Flashpoints%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20Gaza%2C%20Yemen%20and%20Taiwan%20Point%20to%20a%20Global%20War%20in%20the%20Making%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F20120344%2FAnti-terrorist_operation_in_eastern_Ukraine_War_Ukraine_26894689722.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20winning%20the%202020%20election%20on%20a%20platform%20of%20ending%20America%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cforever%20wars%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20withdrawing%20from%20Afghanistan%20in%202021%2C%20Joseph%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20is%20a%20war%20presidency.%20And%20the%20United%20States%20remains%20a%20world%20power%20at%20the%20core%20of%20which%20is%20a%20foreign%20policy%20establishment%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbook-review-david-vine-the-united-states-of-war%5C%22%3Ewedded%20to%20its%20war%20machine%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20war%20mentality%20and%20machine%20is%20the%20bedrock%20of%20Washington%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20to%20sustain%20its%20primacy%20in%20global%20affairs%2C%20as%20its%20global%20positions%20come%20under%20increasing%20pressure%20from%20emerging%20middle-level%20powers%2C%20especially%20China%20and%20its%20allies.%20Thus%2C%20the%20region%20from%20West%20to%20South%20Asia%20is%20now%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20outright%20warfare%20and%20military%20conflict.%20But%20the%20new%20phase%20of%20military%20conflict%20also%20links%20with%20America%E2%80%99s%20proxy%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20stretches%20far%20into%20East%20Asia%2C%20principally%20Taiwan.%20We%20have%20therefore%20the%20emerging%20contours%20of%20global%20military%20conflict%20of%20potentially%20of%20catastrophic%20proportions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20global%20crisis%20of%20the%20US%20world%20system%20combines%20with%20the%20crisis%20of%20US%20power%20at%20home%2C%20as%20the%20world%20watches%20the%20unfolding%20of%20the%202024%20presidential%20election%20campaign.%20On%20the%20home%20front%2C%20the%20US%20faces%20the%20prospect%20of%20a%20potentially%20violent%20conflict%20between%20a%2091-times%20indicted%20and%20twice%20impeached%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20promises%20a%20lawless%20dictatorship%20in%20which%20the%20president%20is%20above%20law%2C%20constitutional%20norms%2C%20and%20democratic%20accountability%2C%20and%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20candidates%20for%20control%20of%20the%20US%20war%20machine%20are%20vying%20with%20one%20another%20as%20to%20who%20is%20the%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2Fdonald-trump-senile-election-campaign-31948125%5C%22%3Esenile%20candidate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0while%20serious%20commentators%20and%20analysts%20are%20asking%20whether%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbook-review-barbara-walter-america-civil-war-fascism%5C%22%3EUS%20is%20descending%20into%20civil%20war%20or%20widespread%20political%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Is%20it%20any%20wonder%20that%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheroadsinitiative.org%2Famerica-in-crisis-will-there-be-a-peaceful-transfer-of-power%2F%5C%22%3Epeaceful%20transfer%20of%20power%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%202025%20is%20in%20jeopardy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWars%20abroad%2C%20political%20violence%20at%20home%3A%20Empires%20usually%20decay%20from%20within%20but%20in%20the%20age%20of%20globalisation%20and%20digitisation%2C%20the%20repercussions%20and%20reverberations%20would%20be%20worldwide.%20In%20such%20conditions%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbook-review-america-militarism%5C%22%3Efear%3C%2Fa%3E%20becomes%20a%20major%20force%20to%20mobilise%20opinion%20behind%20warfare.%20But%20the%20post-1945%20American%20century%20was%20born%20%E2%80%9Cscaring%20hell%E