a%20global%20scale%20pales%20in%20comparison%20with%20American%20capability%20to%20provoke%20and%20sustain%20hostilities%20across%20geographies.%20Other%20states%20can%20launch%20wars%3B%20only%20the%20US%20empire%20can%20extract%20strategic%20mileage%20and%20commercial%20benefits%20from%20wars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11160252%2FGA6xi9-WoAEKSsS.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11160252%2FGA6xi9-WoAEKSsS.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11160252%2FGA6xi9-WoAEKSsS-300x163.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11160252%2FGA6xi9-WoAEKSsS-1024x555.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688654%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20bombed%20locality%20in%20Gaza.%20Photo%3A%20Ashfaq%20Amra%2FUNRWA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmerica%E2%80%99s%20war%20machine%20is%20ravenous%2C%20hence%20its%20readiness%20to%20participate%20in%20every%20big%20and%20small%20war%20stems%20from%20its%20need%20to%20justify%20its%20humongous%20annual%20military%20budget%20of%20over%20%24800%20billion.%20Its%20military-industrial%20complex%20needs%20to%20sell%20lethal%20products%20and%20carry%20out%20live%20trials%20of%20its%20newly%20designed%20weapons.%20But%20even%20these%20factors%20are%20trumped%20by%20the%20US%20foreign%20policy%20establishment%E2%80%99s%20irrational%2C%20but%20growing%2C%20insecurities%20due%20to%20the%20ensuing%20imperial%20%E2%80%98decline%E2%80%99%20amid%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20Eurasian%20continent%20as%20a%20challenge%20to%20its%20sea%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELand%20power%20versus%20sea%20power%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20maritime%20world%20%E2%80%93%20dominated%20first%20by%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20Royal%20Navy%20that%20%E2%80%9Cruled%20the%20waves%E2%80%9D%20(and%20%E2%80%9Cwaived%20the%20rules%E2%80%9D)%2C%20and%20latterly%20by%20US%20naval%20forces%20%E2%80%93%20fears%20being%20outflanked%20by%20the%20combined%20strength%20of%20Germany%2C%20Russia%2C%20and%20China%20forming%20an%20alliance%20across%20the%20Eurasian%20landmass.%20As%20in%20the%20past%2C%20so%20it%20is%20today%3A%20maritime%20powers%20resort%20to%20wars%20to%20break%20emerging%20connectivities%2C%20whether%20it%20was%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20vision%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.dtic.mil%2Fsti%2Fcitations%2FADA138432%5C%22%3EBerlin-Baghdad%20railway%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20World%20War%20I%2C%20or%20any%20Sino-Russian-Iranian%20bloc%20across%20Eurasia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnglo-American%20maritime%20hegemony%20and%20power%20over%20the%20rhythms%20of%20global%20commerce%20are%20under%20stress.%20There%20is%20a%20growing%20clamour%20to%20re-negotiate%20and%20re-envision%20global%20order%20with%20the%20Eurasian%20region%20at%20its%20center%2C%20or%20at%20least%20more%20central%20than%20it%20has%20historically%20been.%20The%20patterns%20of%20competition%2C%20conflict%2C%20and%C2%A0cooperation%20are%20playing%20out%20with%20regard%20to%20connectivity%2C%20trade%2C%20supply%20routes%2C%20and%20resources%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20revival%20of%20rail%20technology.%20The%20old%20Silk%20Road%20replaced%20by%20the%20lightning%20speed%20of%20the%20iron%20and%20steel%20of%20the%20high-speed%20freight%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeographically%2C%20Eurasia%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20expansive%20region%20that%20forms%20a%20land%20bridge%20that%20borders%20Europe%2C%20the%20Asia-Pacific%2C%20West%20Asia%2C%20and%20South%20Asia.%20The%20Eurasian%20Land%20Bridge%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20undermine%20(or%20complement