20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20supporters%20have%20regularly%20protested%20in%20the%20street%2C%20but%20the%20PTI%20party%20has%20also%20faced%20its%20own%20crackdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20mid-January%2C%20a%20Pakistani%20court%20ruled%20that%20the%20party%20must%20drop%20its%20cricket%20bat%20symbol%2C%20effectively%20forcing%20the%20candidates%20to%20run%20as%20independents%20without%20their%20famous%20symbol%20that%20had%20helped%20the%20many%20illiterate%20voters%20identify%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20player%20in%20Pakistani%20politics%20is%20the%20powerful%20military%20that%20has%20held%20the%20reigns%20of%20power%20for%20decades%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20doing%20away%20with%20elections%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%E2%80%99s%20fate%20has%20been%20tied%20to%20his%20relationship%20with%20the%20generals%20who%20once%20favored%20him%20but%20with%20whom%20he%20has%20since%20fallen%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20experience%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Nawaz%20Sharif%2C%20who%20was%20previously%20removed%20from%20power%20and%20who%20fled%20into%20exile%2C%20has%20been%20somewhat%20reversed%20as%20he%20is%20now%20considered%20the%20favorite%20in%20February%E2%80%99s%20vote%20and%20his%20past%20falling%20out%20with%20the%20military%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20forgiven.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpakistan-ex-pm-imran-khan-sentenced-to-10-years%2Fa-68118794%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706610049000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F10123703%2FScreenshot-2023-05-10-at-12.36.54-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-imran-khan-sentenced-ten-years-cypher%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20prime%20minister%20and%20cricket%20legend%20has%20been%20fighting%20legal%20battles%20since%20bein