ions%20on%20single%20judge%20or%20division%20bench%20would%20not%20be%20proper.%20Anything%20we%20say%20will%20have%20(an)%20effect%20on%20impinging%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20high%20court.%20We%20will%20handle%20it%20in%20some%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20appearing%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20state%20government%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20(single%20bench)%20judge%20is%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20rally.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20the%20CJI%20said%20that%20the%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20high%20court%20is%20allocating%20cases%20and%20the%20SC%20would%20not%20like%20to%20%E2%80%9Carrogate%20his%20powers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20matter%20has%20now%20been%20listed%20on%20February%2019.%20The%20parties%20are%20to%20complete%20their%20pleadings%20within%20three%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20apex%20court%20intervention%20came%20following%20Calcutta%20HC%20judge%2C%20Justice%20Abhijit%20Gangopadhyay%E2%80%99s%20outburst%20against%20a%20division%20bench%20judge%2C%20calling%20the%20bench%E2%80%99s%20order%20%E2%80%9Cwholly%20illegal%20and%20has%20to%20be%20ignored%E2%80%9D%20and%20personally%20targeting%20one%20of%20the%20division%20bench%20judges%2C%20Soumen%20Sen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20his%20January%2025%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmercurydocs.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2Fdocs%2FHC_Order_25-01-2024_WBCHCA0449642023_12_22150_2023_16_1_3_HC_16_0.pdf%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fmercurydocs.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2Fdocs%2FHC_Order_25-01-2024_WBCHCA0449642023_12_22150_2023_16_1_3_HC_16_0.pdf%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1706676640085000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw39kLDzKP-_dTj8Lg9_S4rb%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorder%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0regarding%