he%20INDIA%20bloc%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpre-planned%E2%80%9D.%20But%20JD(U)%20leader%20Tyagi%20on%20Monday%20calling%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%98achhoot%E2%80%99%20(untouchable)%20has%20significance%20as%20the%20phrase%20has%20stopped%20being%20used%20for%20deep%2C%20casteist%20resonance%2C%20especially%20given%20that%20Kharge%20himself%20belongs%20to%20a%20Dalit%20community%20from%20Karnataka.%20Untouchability%20has%20been%20abolished%20by%20Article%2017%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20and%20the%20use%20of%20the%20phrase%20itself%20is%20considered%20demeaning%20and%20derogatory%2C%20if%20not%20a%20criminal%20offence%20in%20some%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETyagi%20is%20reported%20to%20have%20said%20that%20had%20the%20exit%20been%20pre-planned%2C%20JD(U)%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20brought%20regional%20allies%20to%20join%20INDIA.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20did%20we%20bring%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20with%20an%20%E2%80%98achhoot%E2%80%99%20party%20like%20you%20(Congress)%3F%E2%80%9D%20quotes%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKharge%20had%20earlier%20said%20that%20the%20move%20was%20aimed%20at%20damaging%C2%A0%20INDIA.%20ANI%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CSuch%20decisions%20cannot%20be%20taken%20in%20a%20hurry%E2%80%A6This%20shows%20that%20it%20was%20all%20pre-planned.%20To%20break%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20they%20(BJP-JD(U))%20planned%20all%20this%E2%80%A6%20He%20(Nitish%20Kumar)%20kept%20us%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20he%20kept%20Lalu%20Yadav%20in%20the%20dark.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETill%20as%20recently%20as%20the%20Karnataka%20elections%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUwEPwA0_yQg%5C%22%3Emade%20allegedly%20receiving%20%E2%80%98abuse%E2%80%99%20(%3Cem%3Egaali%20khaana%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20topic%20he%20raised%20in%20election%20speeches.%20He%20said%20there%20were%2091%20abuses%20hurled%20at%20him%2C%20alluding%20tangentially%20to%20abuse%20as%20being%20casteist%2C%20with%20him%20belonging%20to%20an%20OBC%20community.%20The%20Opposition%20has%20hit%20back%20by%20citing%20instances%20of%20Modi%20calling%20a%20Congress%20MP%E2%80%99s%20partner%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fnarendra-modi-calls-shashi-tharoors-wife-50-crore-rupee-girlfriend%2Farticleshow%2F17008278.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E50%20crore%20ki%20girlfriend%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20and%20other%20derogatory%2C%20personal%20remarks%20about%20senior%20opposition%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%20on%20Sunday%20formed%20a%20government%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20within%20hours%20of%20resigning%20as%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20chief%20minister%2C%20drawing%20widespread%20ire%20across%20the%20political%20spectrum.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706604637000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30141938%2F330914378_733681448348724_4339246958611315245_n.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fleader-from-bjps-latest-ally-jdu-terming-congress-achhoot-raises-serious-questions%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22K.C.%20Tyagi%20was%20ostensibly%20responding%20to%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20saying%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20latest%20flip%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpre-planned%E2%80%9D.%20Untouchability%20was%20abolished%20by%20the%20Indian%20Constitution's%20Article%2017.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fleader-from-bjps-latest-ally-jdu-terming-congress-achhoot-raises-serious-questions%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20hires%20its%20own%20Africa%20army%20to%20succeed%20Wagner's%20mercenaries%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706602545000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107255832%2Cimgsize-74476.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%