amily%20member%20or%20a%20friend%20was%20perhaps%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F319083%2Fkannauj-perfumer-turns-ancestral-home-into-retreat-for-perfume-making-ancient-craft-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperfume%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20in%20Bilimora%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20to%20be%20given%20the%20latest%20perfume%20as%20a%20gift%20from%20abroad%20was%20a%20hot%20topic%20amongst%20Mohamadadil%20Asif%20Malkani%2C%20fondly%20called%20Adil%2C%20and%20his%20friends.%20These%20discussions%20and%20the%20whiffs%20of%20these%20perfumes%20left%20a%20deep%20impact%20on%20the%20young%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20started%20his%20eponymous%20perfume%20venture%20selling%20%3Cem%3EAttars%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20perfumes%20in%202019%2C%20his%20goal%20was%20to%20offer%20the%20same%20premium%20fragrance%20to%20customers%20at%20home.%20Starting%20with%20his%20father%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20an%20%3Cem%3EAttar%3C%2Fem%3E%20company%20for%20over%20three%20decades%2C%20the%20entrepreneur%E2%80%99s%20vision%20was%20to%20make%20traditional%20fragrance%20appealing%20to%20the%20younger%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttar%20or%20%3Cem%3Eittar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20is%20said%20to%20have%20been%20derived%20from%20the%20Persian%20word%20%3Cem%3Eitir%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewhich%20means%20perfume.%20Working%20out%20of%20his%20home%2C%20Adil%20spent%20months%20perfecting%20the%20formulations%20and%20fragrances%20which%20would%20be%20liked%20by%20his%20buyers.%20He%20would%20send%20free%20samples%20to%20friends%20and%20family%20in%20Bilimora%20and%20make%20changes%20as%20per%20their%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Class%205%20dropout%20used%20his%20business%20acumen%20and%20digital%20marketing%20skills%20to%20build%20a%20good%20website%20and%20get%20word%20out.%20Starting%20with%2020%20orders%20in%202019%2C%20Adil%20Qadri%20has%20sold%20over%2014%20lakh%20orders%20so%20far%20with%20a%20m