ed%20to%20make%20a%20name%20for%20himself.%20He%20started%20doing%20computer%20and%20mobile%20repairing%20courses%20and%20worked%20in%20a%20few%20local%20shops.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20turning%20point%20in%20his%20life%20came%20in%202014%2C%20when%20his%20uncle%20told%20him%20about%20SEO%20(Search%20Engine%20Optimisation).%20%E2%80%9CHe%20told%20me%20that%20SEO%20was%20the%20future%20and%20that%20I%20should%20learn%20it%20and%20website%20designing%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Adil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_348609935_624470889703121_3856307365791923769_n_1080-1706535533.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Adil%20at%20one%20of%20his%20stores%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_348609935_624470889703121_3856307365791923769_n_1080-1706535533.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_348609935_624470889703121_3856307365791923769_n_1080-1706535533-300x294.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_348609935_624470889703121_3856307365791923769_n_1080-1706535533-500x490.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_348609935_624470889703121_3856307365791923769_n_1080-1706535533-768x753.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_348609935_624470889703121_3856307365791923769_n_1080-1706535533-150x147.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339991%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221059%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAdil%20at%20one%20of%20his%2015%20stores%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdil%20first%20built%20a%20m