taff%20further.%20After%20all%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20real%20form%20of%20recognition%20for%20our%20work.%20As%20an%20officer%2C%20I%20can%20be%20a%20role%20model%20for%20them.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20speaking%20about%20playing%20a%20real-life%20character%2C%20Imran%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20you%20portray%20a%20living%20person%20in%20a%20performance%2C%20it%20becomes%20an%20authoritative%20portrayal%20of%20their%20experiences%3A%20their%20motivations%2C%20the%20challenges%20they%20confronted%2C%20and%20how%20they%20overcame%20their%20struggles.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_408791019_1441618009726504_8932941298547774044_n_1080-1706533714.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Playing%20the%20role%20of%20a%20real-life%20IPS%20officer%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_408791019_1441618009726504_8932941298547774044_n_1080-1706533714.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_408791019_1441618009726504_8932941298547774044_n_1080-1706533714-300x196.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_408791019_1441618009726504_8932941298547774044_n_1080-1706533714-500x327.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_408791019_1441618009726504_8932941298547774044_n_1080-1706533714-768x503.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_408791019_1441618009726504_8932941298547774044_n_1080-1706533714-150x98.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339963%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EImran%20Zahid%20(on%20the%20right)%20walking%20with%20filmmaker%20Mahesh%20Bhatt.%20The%20actor%20will%20play%20an%20IPS%20officer%20in%20his%20upcoming%20film.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChoosing%20IPS%20over%20medicine%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Guntur%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F229261%2Fandhra-pradesh-cyclone-safe-chutillu-home-construction-mud-sustainable-low-cost-traditional-india-ser106%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%20(AP)%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20grew%20up%20in%20an%20upper-middle-class%20family%20where%20his%20father%20served%20as%20an%20officer%20in%20the%20customs%20and%20central%20excise%20department%2C%20while%20his%20mother%20was%20a%20homemaker.%20Like%20thousands%20of%20youngsters%20in%20AP%2C%20his%20initial%20goal%20was%20to%20become%20a%20doctor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20his%20third%20year%20of%20medical%20school%20studying%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F244472%2Fneet-result-2020-mumbai-slums-mbbs-govandi-rushda-praveen-khan-government-college-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMBBS%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20decided%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20central%20civil%20services%20exam.%20However%2C%20what%20inspired%20this%20decision%20was%20a%20personal%20tragedy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20studying%20at%20the%20Andhra%20Medical%20College%20in%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20his%20brother-in-law%20was%20murdered%20following%20a%20business%20rivalry.%20A%20shocking%20development%2C%20it%20left%20his%20family%20dealing%20with%20a%20crisis.%20But%2C%20amid%20this%20crisis%2C%20he%20saw%20something%20that%20would%20leave%20an%20indelible%20impression.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20many%20influential%20people%20with%20notorious%20criminal%20backgrounds%20involved%20in%20this%20murder%20case.%20Fortunately%2C%20we%20had%20a%20very%20good%20police%20officer%20who%20fairly%20investigated%20the%20case.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20I%20saw%20the%20best%20of%20what%20a%20police%20officer%20can%20do%20and%20the%20impact%20they%20can%20have%20on%20our%20society.%20As%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20law%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20help%20our%20family%2C%20manage%20other%20professionals%20engaged%20in%20this%20investigation%2C%20and%20nab%20the%20culprits%20as%20well.%20Instead%20of%20becoming%20a%20doctor%2C%20I%20felt%20I%20could%20be%20more%20useful%20to%20society%20as%20a%20police%20officer%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Dr%20Naik.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Dr%20Naik%20struggles%20to%20recall%20the%20name%20of%20the%20officer%20who%20solved%20his%20brother-in-law%E2%80%99s%20murder%20more%20than%2030%20years%20after%20it%20happened%2C%20he%20cannot%20forget%20the%20impression%20the%20episode%20left%20behind.%20Of%20course%2C%20with%20other%20family%20members%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20service%20motivating%20him%20to%20make%20that%20transition%20to%20a%20career%20in%20the%20IPS%2C%20this%20memory%20remained%20seared%20in%20his%20consciousness.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20MBBS%20in%201996%2C%20he%20served%20as%20a%20doctor%20for%20three%20years%20until%201999%20when%20he%20decided%20that%20he%20needed%20a%20complete%20shift%20away%20from%20a%20career%20in%20medicine.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20my%20third%20year%20onwards%2C%20I%20began%20preparing%20for%20the%20UPSC%20exam.%20I%20was%20simultaneously%20studying%20for%20my%20MBBS%20and%20preparing%20for%20the%20Union%20Civil%20Services%20exam.%20Following%20my%20MBBS%2C%20I%20worked%20at%20a%20private%20hospital%20in%20Visakhapatnam%20for%20a%20short%20while%20before%20leaving%20for%20Hyderabad%20to%20join%20UPSC%20coaching%20classes.%20To%20support%20myself%20financially%2C%20however%2C%20I%20even%20worked%20at%20the%20Apollo%20Hospital%20in%20Jubilee%20Hills%20as%20an%20emergency%20physician%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20decision%20to%20quit%20medicine%20and%20prepare%20%5Bfull-time%5D%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F308203%2Fhow-to-prepare-for-upsc-cse-for-working-professionals-ias-divya-mittal-shares-tips-on-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUPSC%20exam%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20met%20by%20vehement%20opposition%20in%20the%20family.%20They%20wanted%20me%20to%20continue%20as%20a%20doctor%20and%20earn%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20attempt%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20reached%20the%20interview%20stage%20but%20missed%20out.%20But%20helping%20him%20along%20the%20way%20were%20a%20few%20friends%20he%20had%20known%20since%20primary%20school.%20They%20were%20also%20preparing%20for%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20supported%20me%20a%20lot.%20They%20could%20not%20get%20through%20but%20they%20were%20happy%20that%20I%20did%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20faith%20in%20Dr%20Naik%20would%20eventually%20pay%20off%20as%20he%20cleared%20the%20interview%20stage%20in%20his%20next%20attempt.%20He%20joined%20the%20IPS%20in%202002%20as%20part%20of%20the%20DANIPS%20(Delhi%2C%20Andaman%20%26amp%3B%20Nicobar%20Islands%2C%20Lakshadweep%2C%20Dadra%2C%20and%20Nagar%20Haveli%20and%20Daman%20and%20Diu%20Police%20Service)%20cadre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20becoming%20an%20IPS%20officer%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20has%20gone%20on%20to%20achieve%20a%20great%20deal.%20From%20receiving%20a%20special%20commendation%20from%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%20for%20organising%20relief%20operations%20after%20Cyclone%20HUD%20HUD%20in%202014%20to%20investigating%20and%20extraditing%20Sanjeev%20Chawla%2C%20the%20bookmaker%20famously%20involved%20with%20the%20deceased%20cricket%20player%20Hansie%20Cronje%2C%20in%20fixing%20matches%20between%20India%20and%20South%20Africa%20in%202000%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20has%20many%20achievements%20to%20his%20name.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20notable%20achievements%20include%20initiating%20the%20modernisation%20process%20of%20the%20Lakshadweep%20Police%20during%20his%20first%20official%20posting%20and%20investigating%20and%20solving%20the%202008%20bomb%20blasts%20in%20the%20M-Block%20Market%20of%20Greater%20Kailash%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20In%202018%2C%20he%20also%20solved%20the%20paper%20leak%20case%20of%20the%20CBSE%20Class%2012%20economics%20and%20Class%2010%20mathematics%20examinations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20he%20won%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Police%20Medal%20for%20Gallantry%20in%20January%202021%20for%20conducting%20a%20daring%20rescue%20operation%20of%20a%20kidnapped%205-year-old%20boy%20in%20Sahibabad%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(UP).%20During%20his%20career%2C%20he%20has%20investigated%20a%20plethora%20of%20cases%20but%20this%20one%20stands%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERam%20Gopal%20Naik%2C%20DCP%20Crime%20Branch%3A%20Delhi%20Police%20Crime%20Branch%20with%20help%20of%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20and%20Home%20Affairs%20was%20trying%20to%20get%20him%20(Sanjeev%20Chawla).In%202013%2C%20extradition%20process%20started.%20We%20have%20got%2012-days%20custody.We%20have%20not%20yet%20questioned%20him%2Cprocess%20will%20start%20now.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FI4yOF3swVS%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FI4yOF3swVS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1227948459468025856%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2013%2C%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERescuing%20a%20child%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2025%20January%202018%2C%20as%20preparations%20for%20that%20year%E2%80%99s%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations%20were%20in%20full%20force%2C%20a%20five-year-old%20son%20of%20a%20prominent%20businessman%20in%20Northeast%20Delhi%20was%20kidnapped.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fdelhi-police-crack-daring-kidnapping-12-day-hunt-ends-in-gunfire-and-a-rescued-child-5054121%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20the%20kidnapping%2C%20the%20accused%20conducted%20a%20recce%20of%20the%20area%20for%20over%20a%20month%20and%20decided%20to%20target%20the%20school%20bus.%20They%20made%20three%20failed%20attempts%20on%20January%2021%2C%2022%20and%2023.%E2%80%9D%20Speaking%20to%20the%20media%2C%20the%20then%20JCP%20(Crime%20Branch)%20Alok%20Kumar%20identified%20the%20accused%20as%20Nitin%20Sharma%2C%20Ravi%20Kumar%2C%20and%20Pankaj%20alias%20Singh%20Saheb.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20three%20suspects%20had%20hatched%20a%20plan%20to%20kidnap%20the%20child%20after%20%E2%80%9CSunny%20Gupta%2C%20father%20of%20the%20child%2C%20recently%20finalised%20a%20real%20estate%20deal%20of%20Rs%2060%20lakh.%20The%20details%20of%20the%20deal%20were%20common%20knowledge%20of%20everyone%20who%20stayed%20in%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20locality%20GTB%20Enclave.%20Nitin%20thought%20he%20could%20earn%20a%20good%20ransom%20if%20he%20kidnapped%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20son.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20morning%20of%2025%20January%2C%20when%20the%20school%20van%20was%20approaching%20the%20school%2C%20the%20kidnappers%20intercepted%20it%20and%20snatched%20the%20boy%20for%20ransom.%20The%20kidnappers%20shot%20the%20driver%20in%20the%20leg%20and%20took%20the%20boy%20to%20a%20two-bedroom%20flat%20in%20Sahibabad%E2%80%99s%20Shalimar%20City%20apartments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20working%20as%20DCP%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20Crime%20Branch.%20Initially%2C%20the%20case%20was%20taken%20up%20by%20the%20local%20police.%20For%20a%20week%2C%20the%20local%20police%20could%20not%20get%20any%20leads.%20Given%20that%20the%20incident%20happened%20a%20day%20before%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247811%2Frepublic-day-president-address-to-the-nation-speech-constitution-ram-nath-kovind-abdul-kalam-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERepublic%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20Commissioner%20to%20solve%20this%20case%20and%20rescue%20the%20boy.%20My%20commissioner%20took%20a%20call%20that%20the%20case%20should%20be%20transferred%20to%20the%20Crime%20Branch%20and%20I%20was%20selected%20to%20handle%20this%20sensitive%20investigation%20given%20that%20a%20boy%E2%80%99s%20life%20was%20at%20stake%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20Dr%20Naik%E2%80%99s%20team%20took%20over%20the%20case%2C%20they%20deployed%20their%20sources%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20brought%20on%20officers%20with%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20knowledge%20of%20criminal%20networks%20in%20Northeast%20Delhi%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20our%20officers%20eventually%20got%20a%20lead%20that%20three%20persons%20were%20missing%20in%20the%20area%20where%20the%20boy%20was%20picked%20up%20and%20that%20they%20may%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20case.%20We%20also%20went%20through%20their%20criminal%20records%20and%20posited%20that%20they%20could%20be%20involved.%20Meanwhile%2C%20we%20also%20kept%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20father%20of%20the%20boy%20who%20was%20receiving%20calls%20for%20a%20ransom.%20Besides%20these%20calls%2C%20he%20was%20also%20receiving%20videos%20%5Bon%20WhatsApp%5D%20of%20the%20kidnappers%20claiming%20that%20they%20have%20his%20son%20and%20voice%20recordings%20too%20where%20he%20could%20hear%20his%20son%20pleading%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98Papa%2C%20I%20love%20you%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20dealing%20with%20kidnappers%2C%20they%20also%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20terrified%20father.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20probably%20felt%20that%20cooperating%20with%20the%20police%20would%20put%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20life%20at%20risk.%20Thus%2C%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20being%20very%20cooperative.%20The%20kidnappers%20had%20demanded%20Rs%2060%20lakh%20as%20ransom%20and%20we%20asked%20him%20to%20negotiate%20to%20buy%20some%20time%20and%20trace%20these%20calls.%20But%20we%20believe%20he%20was%20actively%20hiding%20things%20from%20us.%20We%20discovered%20that%20he%20was%20even%20arranging%20the%20money%20to%20pay%20off%20the%20kidnappers%20so%20that%20his%20child%20could%20come%20back%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20recalls%20that%20his%20team%20%E2%80%9Cengaged%20in%20some%20ethical%20hacking%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20father%E2%80%99s%20phone%20so%20that%20they%20could%20have%20first-hand%20information%20about%20what%20was%20being%20discussed.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20kidnappers%20set%20a%20date%20and%20location%20for%20the%20exchange.%20After%20this%20conversation%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20took%20the%20father%20into%20confidence%20and%20assured%20him%20that%20they%20would%20rescue%20his%20child.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestatesman.com%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fkidnapper-shot-dead-two-held-5-year-old-rescued-1502580909.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Statesman%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20ransom%20calls%20were%20also%20made%20from%20nearby%20areas%20we%20selected%20a%20few%20areas%20and%20kept%20a%20close%20watch%20on%20a%20few%20suspects%20there.%20Meanwhile%2C%20through%20local%20sources%20and%20technical%20surveillance%2C%20police%20identified%20Nitin%20as%20a%20prime%20suspect.%20Police%20kept%20track%20of%20his%20activities%20and%20deployed%20sources%20to%20keep%20a%20closer%20watch%20on%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20shared%20Nitin%E2%80%99s%20pictures%20with%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20he%20identified%20him%20as%20a%20frequent%20visitor%20of%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20Naik%20noted.%20After%20a%20thorough%20investigation%2C%20he%20was%20identified%20as%20one%20of%20the%20kidnappers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20taking%20the%20father%20into%20confidence%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20learned%20that%20Nitin%20was%20attending%20a%20wedding%20in%20Northeast%20Delhi.%20In%20response%20to%20this%20news%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20and%20his%20team%20attended%20this%20wedding%20pretending%20to%20be%20guests.%20At%20the%20wedding%20venue%2C%20one%20of%20the%20officers%20identified%20the%20main%20suspect.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20they%20thought%20of%20nabbing%20him%20there%20but%20decided%20against%20this%20move%20because%20of%20the%20commotion%20it%20would%20create.%20Instead%2C%20they%20trailed%20his%20car%20out%20of%20the%20venue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20conversation%20with%20The%20Statesman%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CPolice%20started%20following%20Nitin%20from%208%20pm%20%5Bon%205%20February%202018%5D%20till%2012.30%20midnight%20%5Bwhen%20he%20was%20intercepted%5D.%20He%20was%20driving%20his%20Swift%20at%20speeds%20close%20to%2090%20km%2Fhr%20to%20100km%2Fhr.%20Police%20followed%20him%20on%20four%20bikes%20and%20four%20vans.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20main%20suspect%20dropped%20his%20girlfriend%20at%20her%20residence%2C%20the%20police%20continued%20trailing%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestatesman.com%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fkidnapper-shot-dead-two-held-5-year-old-rescued-1502580909.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Dr%20Naik%20added%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CAround%2012.30%20am%2C%20Nitin%20was%20intercepted%20near%20a%20community%20block%20in%20Seemapuri%20%5Bnear%20the%20Delhi-UP%20border%5D.%20Before%20his%20vehicle%20stopped%2C%20he%20hit%20our%20vehicle%20and%20he%20was%20drunk.%20He%20was%20also%20carrying%20three%20mobile%20phones.%20On%20interrogation%2C%20he%20told%20police%20that%20two%20of%20his%20friends%20had%20kept%20the%20child%20in%20a%20flat%20in%20Shalimar%20City%20in%20Sahibabad.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20the%20main%20suspect%20to%20confess%20where%20they%20were%20keeping%20the%20boy%2C%20there%20were%20discussions%20among%20senior%20officers%20who%20were%20informed%20of%20the%20interception%20that%20they%20should%20wait%20to%20gather%20more%20force%20(personnel).%20Dr%20Naik%20disagreed%20and%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20time%20and%20they%20needed%20to%20move%20fast%20with%20the%20suspect%20in%20their%20custody.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20his%20phones%20are%20with%20us%20and%20if%20he%20is%20unreachable%2C%20his%20accomplices%20may%20get%20alerted%2C%20leave%20the%20apartment%2C%20and%20possibly%20harm%20the%20boy%20as%20well.%20Thankfully%2C%20my%20top%20boss%20at%20the%20Delhi%20Crime%20Branch%20trusted%20my%20instincts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Ram-Gopal-Naik-IPS-Officer-Image-5-1706534343.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Serving%20IPS%20officer%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Ram-Gopal-Naik-IPS-Officer-Image-5-1706534343.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Ram-Gopal-Naik-IPS-Officer-Image-5-1706534343-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Ram-Gopal-Naik-IPS-Officer-Image-5-1706534343-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Ram-Gopal-Naik-IPS-Officer-Image-5-1706534343-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Ram-Gopal-Naik-IPS-Officer-Image-5-1706534343-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339981%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDCP%20Dr%20Ram%20Gopal%20Naik%2C%20a%202002-batch%20IPS%20officer%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20barely%201.5%20hours%2C%20Dr%20Naik%E2%80%99s%20team%20reached%20the%20apartment%20complex%2C%20did%20a%20complete%20recce%20of%20it%2C%20covered%20all%20the%20exits%2C%20got%20into%20the%20flat%20amidst%20a%20firefight%2C%20and%20rescued%20the%20boy.%20To%20understand%20the%20layout%20of%20the%20two-bedroom%20apartment%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20and%20two%20other%20officers%20visited%20another%20apartment%20in%20the%20same%20complex%20and%20asked%20the%20family%20residing%20inside%20if%20they%20could%20take%20a%20look.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20we%20understood%20the%20layout%20of%20this%20apartment%2C%20we%20took%20positions%20outside%20the%20fifth-floor%20flat%20where%20the%20child%20was%20being%20kept.%20Meanwhile%2C%20we%20also%20had%20a%20team%20prepared%20below%20with%20blankets%20and%20nets%20ready%20in%20case%20the%20kidnappers%20tried%20to%20throw%20the%20boy%20off%20the%20balcony.%20At%20this%20crucial%20juncture%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20send%20the%20suspect%20to%20ring%20the%20bell%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20suspect%20Nitin%20proceeded%20to%20ring%20the%20bell%2C%20but%20the%20moment%20his%20accomplice%20opened%20the%20door%20he%20sensed%20that%20something%20was%20wrong%20and%20tried%20to%20shut%20it%20immediately.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20he%20was%20about%20to%20shut%20the%20door%2C%20I%20told%20one%20of%20my%20officers%20that%20we%20had%20to%20break%20these%20doors%20down.%20Luckily%2C%20there%20was%20a%20little%20gap%20on%20top%20of%20the%20iron%20grill%20door.%20One%20of%20my%20officers%20was%20able%20to%20bend%20the%20iron%20grill%20part%20of%20the%20door%20down%20and%20that%20left%20enough%20space%20for%20me%20to%20enter.%20Following%20this%2C%20the%20kidnappers%20inside%20began%20firing%20at%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20As%20per%20news%20reports%2C%20a%20bullet%20hit%20Inspector%20Vinay%20Tyagi%E2%80%99s%20vest%2C%20while%20another%20hit%20commando%20Kuldip%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20this%20chaos%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20climbed%20over%20the%20bent%20iron%20grill%20and%20took%20a%20peek%20at%20the%20gap%20left%20behind%20by%20a%20second%20wooden%20door%20inside%20to%20see%20if%20the%20child%20was%20inside%20the%20main%20hall%20of%20the%20flat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20found%20that%20the%20boy%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20there.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20ordered%20the%20personnel%20behind%20me%20to%20fire%20back.%20There%20was%20an%20exchange%20of%20fire.%20One%20of%20the%20kidnappers%20was%20shot%20down%20on%20the%20ground%20lying%20in%20a%20pool%20of%20blood%20while%20the%20other%20was%20shot%20in%20the%20leg.%20My%20team%20immediately%20followed%20me%20inside%20while%20I%20went%20straight%20to%20the%20bedroom%20to%20find%20the%20child%20under%20a%20blanket%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuffice%20it%20to%20say%2C%20the%20child%20was%20terrified%20following%20the%20exchange%20of%20fire%20outside.%20%E2%80%9CI%20slowly%20took%20down%20the%20blanket%20and%20told%20him%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Beta%2C%20mein%20police%20uncle%20hoon.%20Mein%20tumhare%20papa%20ke%20paas%20le%20jaane%20ke%20liye%20aaya%20hoon.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20After%20hearing%20those%20words%2C%20he%20immediately%20jumped%20off%20the%20bed%20and%20hugged%20me.%20I%20carried%20him%20out%20of%20the%20flat%20covering%20his%20eyes.%20As%20we%20were%20driving%20to%20GTB%20Hospital%2C%20I%20called%20up%20his%20father%20and%20told%20him%20that%20we%20had%20rescued%20his%20child%20safely.%20This%20was%20around%202%20am%20in%20the%20wee%20hours%20%5Bof%206%20February%202018%5D.%20The%20father%20was%20asleep%20when%20we%20called%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20among%20the%20other%20two%20suspects%20inside%20the%20flat%2C%20one%20was%20killed%20while%20the%20other%20was%20injured.%20The%20police%20personnel%20injured%20by%20gunshots%20were%20saved%20by%20their%20bulletproof%20vests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20us%20made%20our%20way%20to%20GTB%20Hospital.%20After%20the%20doctor%20on%20duty%20confirmed%20that%20the%20child%20had%20not%20suffered%20any%20serious%20injuries%20or%20abuse%2C%20the%20parents%20took%20him%20into%20their%20arms.%20It%20was%20an%20emotional%20moment%20seeing%20these%20tearful%20parents%20reuniting%20with%20their%20son.%20I%20also%20shed%20a%20tear.%20Four%20officers%2C%20including%20me%2C%20received%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Police%20Medal%20for%20Gallantry%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20life%20of%20a%20police%20officer%20has%20its%20share%20of%20controversy%20and%20disappointments%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20moments%20like%20these%20that%20make%20the%20journey%20worth%20it.%20Seeing%20that%20tearful%20reunion%20between%20the%20parents%20and%20their%20son%2C%20%E2%80%9Cand%20the%20fact%20that%20you%20made%20it%20possible%E2%80%9D%2C%20is%20what%20makes%20this%20path%20worth%20it.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20Dr%20Ram%20Gopal%20Naik%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22norefe